{"tid":1353240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個感化藍絲方法","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T08:27:55.000Z","uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"912920e0bc81d0ea86381cb18047239801e5ceed","tid":1353240,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:27:13.000Z","msg":"加油。<br />\n説服家人就多更多戰友<br />\n一傳十十傳伯<br />\n<br />\n問下佢，叫佢提議下<br />\n1. 政府過去紀錄惡劣無誠信例子<br />\n&gt;唔抗爭可以做咩反送中<br />\n<br />\n2. 你知唔知返對緊嘅修例講咩<br />\n&gt;你知道嗎，新一代喜歡中國文化不代表喜歡中共<br />\n<br />\n3. 有人收錢，煽動，外國睇戲<br />\n關我咩事？<br />\n我在創造一個大家想要的未來。<br />\n我知反對緊咩<br />\n<br />\n4. 點為香港好<br />\n長遠好定短期好？<br />\n經濟差？扭曲發展嘅金鋪藥房經濟差<br />\n喺咪可以押低租金，大家創業成本平返<br />\n無人投資係警示威者定驚被送中"},{"pid":"1fb4896972524e0a9dc189014d8a96594cc6fe26","tid":1353240,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:39:49.000Z","msg":"我係一個揸單程證落黎嘅大陸女人...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1353162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1353162</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cd338fa94dbfe4c66553b54470716e4945d6452a","tid":1353240,"uid":126142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:41:41.000Z","msg":"你撐警黑 連人都不如<br />\n講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3dc02c15e61748403b2a7002eb01294529224f7","tid":1353240,"uid":260428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd338fa94dbfe4c66553b54470716e4945d6452a","tid":1353240,"uid":126142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:41:41.000Z","msg":"你撐警黑 連人都不如<br />\n講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}